        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How it works",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Your bottle uses a <strong>natural gemstone point</strong> placed inside a BPA-free glass chamber. As the water sits around the crystal, it becomes <strong>energetically structured</strong>, meaning:</p><ul><li>The vibrational field of the crystal interacts with the molecular clusters of water<br/></li><li>Water absorbs energetic resonance (a concept supported in vibrational medicine)<br/></li><li>Drinking this water helps your body shift into a calmer, clearer state<br/></li></ul><p>This is why people describe it as feeling like <strong>“hydration with intention.”</strong></p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_RDaXPM": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Instructions",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "star",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<ol><li><strong>Rinse the bottle</strong> before first use<br/></li><li>Fill with <strong>fresh, filtered water</strong><br/></li><li>Hold the bottle for 5 seconds and <strong>set an intention</strong> (optional but powerful)<br/></li><li>Sip throughout the day—<strong>you’ll naturally drink more water</strong><br/></li><li>Clean weekly; the crystal is removable for easy washing<br/></li></ol><p>Works with: still water, infused water (lemon, mint), or room-temperature tea.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
