          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Activate Natural Healing. Backed by Science.",
            "title_highlight_color": "#6d388b",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_kqeU8Q": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Crystal Energy-Infused Water Bottle is designed for those who want more than ordinary hydration. Each bottle holds a <strong>hand-selected gemstone</strong> known for its unique energetic properties — Rose Quartz for love & softness, Amethyst for calmness, Fluorite for clarity, Smoky Quartz for grounding, and Obsidian for protection.</p><p>Every sip becomes a <strong>mindful ritual</strong>. Instead of drinking water on autopilot, you create a moment of calm, intention, and alignment. Customers say this simple daily habit supports a more centered mood, better sleep, and noticeably more emotional clarity.</p><p>Built with premium glass and stainless steel, the bottle is durable, aesthetically beautiful, and intentionally designed to keep your crystal purified, protected, and energetically potent.</p><p>This is hydration — <em>elevated.</em></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_Gge7Dr",
